Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不敢相信，我以為這會很容易\NI can't believe that I thought it'd be easy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我想，沒人是完美\NWell I guess that no one's perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我被所謂的作夢給欺騙\NI was deceived by a thing we call dreamin'
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.05,0:00:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因為，我想一夢不醒\N'Cause I thought I couldn't hurt it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}現在看看我，是不是很清晰\NNow look at me, it's so easy to see
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}有什麼在隱藏我所求\NSomething's hidin' what I asked for
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.99,0:00:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}歲月飛去\NIt's been years now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.77,0:00:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而我還才漸漸知道\NAnd I'm still seekin' it out
Comment: 0,0:00:36.24,0:00:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,## 副歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}也許，我是卡那在\NMaybe I'm only stuck
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自己，的那片雲上\Non my own cloud above
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.05,0:00:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}也許沒怎樣\NMaybe it's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}也許我瘋狂\Nmaybe I'm insane
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}也許它就是得這麼艱難\NMaybe it's meant to be so tough
